        <h3>What is the SVT Språkplay?</h3>
        <p>SVT Språkplay is a free app to learn swedish and watch TV at the same time. With SVT Språkplay, you can watch your favourite SVT programs with interactive subtitles that come with language support to 18 different languages.</p>
      </div>
