        <p>With SVT Språkplay, learning Swedish is fast, easy and efficient. You can watch your favourite SVT programs and read the text in Swedish with the help of our integrated language support to <b>18 languages</b>. If there is a word you do not understand, tap on it and see the translation.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="../assets/images/languages.png" alt="">
